Comment: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.25,Alternative,Mom,0,0,0,,Man!
Comment: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.80,Alternative,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Come on.
Comment: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.04,Alternative,Mom,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:33.94,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Comment: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.15,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Counting on you.
Comment: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.37,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,They're at the station now.
