Comment: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.25,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,I-I need to calm—
Comment: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.66,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:50.54,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You are to be in charge of our next customer, Nako.
