Comment: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.09,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better to have Ohana,
Comment: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,someone related to her, be her attendant?
Comment: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.89,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,No, that's out of the question.
Comment: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.64,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Then how about you taking the position yourself?!
Comment: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.06,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Same goes for me.
Comment: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:11.56,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I might attempt to slap her if I see her.
Comment: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:17.82,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Geez, why did Ohana have to go and bring an enemy?
