Comment: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.54,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Comment: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.88,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Despite the circumstances, she's still a customer.
Comment: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:34.13,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn will operate as usual.
Comment: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.38,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Though I don't know how\N I'm going to react to everything.
Comment: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.51,Default,All,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
