Comment: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.27,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ride, Tooru!
Comment: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.02,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,No problem.
Comment: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.48,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wow, nothing's changed.
Comment: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:56.23,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Actually, it's gotten a lot older and trashier.
Comment: 0,0:02:59.24,0:02:59.95,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.41,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You haven't changed either, Mom!
Comment: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.53,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Actually, you've gotten a lot older and...
Comment: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop there.
Comment: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.91,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.67,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, god! The young master!
Comment: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.25,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Oh—
Comment: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.09,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You've put on some weight!
Comment: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:20.26,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,A-Allow me to escort you to your room, ma'am.
Comment: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.64,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.55,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Please wait, ma'am!
