Comment: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.56,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,So that's her...
Comment: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.60,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Comment: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.40,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,We've returned.
Comment: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.31,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Ohana?
Comment: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:45.28,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,So the yukata design hasn't changed either.
Comment: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.41,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,There are places nowadays where they let customers pick from a few designs.
Comment: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:52.21,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I think it's important to have things like that too.
Comment: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.17,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Comment: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.55,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Oh, please have some tea.
Comment: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.93,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I think you can improve this, too.
Comment: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.76,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Like, for example, these snacks.
Comment: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.80,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.22,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,This area is known for its Yuzu.
Comment: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.73,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Serving a yuzu-flavored snack would create
Comment: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a topic of discussion between\N the waitress and the customer.
Comment: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.69,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Comment: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.65,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I tend to speak to myself a lot, because of what I do for work.
Comment: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.98,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Comment: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:20.86,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,N-Not at all...
Comment: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:21.78,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.41,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wow...
Comment: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.74,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Comment: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.49,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You have such pretty eyes!
Comment: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.79,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Geez, will you calm down?
Comment: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:37.00,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I can't! I just can't!
Comment: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.55,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You don't know how scary she is, Tomoe.
Comment: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:45.43,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,She made me do all of her summer vacation homework,
Comment: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:49.68,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,and took my New Year's money!
Comment: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.10,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that explains why you like Takako, someone with a similar personality.
Comment: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.48,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,N-No!
Comment: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.48,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Nako!
Comment: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.53,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,How was she?!
Comment: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.78,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,She's a wonderful person.
Comment: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:09.66,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,She gave me so much advice\N on how to make this inn better.
Comment: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.95,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Advice?
Comment: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:11.91,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.25,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,About yukatas and the tea snacks...
Comment: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.00,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Wait—
Comment: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.46,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Don't.
Comment: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.34,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,So what?
Comment: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.92,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'm not writing them down\N because it's what my sister said.
Comment: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.38,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's as an opinion of a cust—
Comment: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.01,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Comment: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.22,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,You're so hardworking, Ohana.
Comment: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.89,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,You just returned and are already back to work.
Comment: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Just returned?
Comment: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:39.90,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.19,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Comment: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.07,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I returned...
Comment: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.58,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So suddenly, to my regular self.
Comment: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.83,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,The me that was holding placards in Tokyo,
Comment: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.58,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,and the me who was having dinner with Ko...
Comment: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.59,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,They're not my regular self.
Comment: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:06.38,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,The me who works here has become my regular self.
Comment: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.22,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Hello, waitress!
Comment: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.18,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,There's a place I want to visit!
Comment: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you accompany me?
Comment: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.85,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,W-Why me?
Comment: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.69,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's scary to climb a hill with heels on.
Comment: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.36,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What are you going to do if something happens
Comment: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to a customer after ignoring her plea?
Comment: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.45,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,There really is nothing here, is there?!
Comment: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.99,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,But there's this thing called a\N Bonbori Festival around here.
Comment: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.83,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's the one thing I liked about this place.
Comment: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:41.83,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,They say your wish comes true, and I believed them.
Comment: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.71,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Did you know about that?
Comment: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.88,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Since forever.
Comment: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:49.22,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask the gods to\N restore your relationship with Ko?
Comment: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:56.10,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\an8}W-W-W-W—
Comment: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.97,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, did I guess correctly?
Comment: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.10,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}did{\i0} get dumped by him.
Comment: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.44,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Got dumped?!
Comment: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.61,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Comment: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.23,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,There are so many other boys out there.
Comment: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.40,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're a little short and thick,
Comment: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.99,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,but since you're my daughter—
Comment: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.74,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Don't...
Comment: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.29,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Don't suddenly start acting like a mother!
Comment: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.16,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm going back now.
Comment: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.66,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wait, Ohana.
Comment: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.17,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.30,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I came to this inn because you speak so highly of it.
Comment: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.67,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You get it, right?
Comment: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.68,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's no time to be depressed\N because you got dumped by some guy.
Comment: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.22,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You'd better show me what's so great about this inn.
Comment: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.65,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I guess her situation with him is worse than I'd thought.
Comment: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.86,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,"It's no time to be depressed\N because you got dumped by some guy."
Comment: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.37,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Dumped by...
Comment: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.96,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Dumped...
Comment: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.08,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Did I really?
Comment: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.63,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So this is what it means to be dumped?
Comment: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.26,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Comment: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.39,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,We've been had.
Comment: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.60,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.19,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Tooru, I need you to make the stock{dashi}.
Comment: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.19,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.61,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It smells so good!
Comment: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.53,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Being this time of the year,\N are you cooking smelt-whiting?
Comment: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.11,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Or is it tempura?
Comment: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:36.62,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,You might laugh, saying that it's "plain boring", but...
Comment: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.37,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh?
Comment: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.66,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Predicting is the same thing as hoping.
Comment: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.83,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's not nice to kill my hopes like that.
Comment: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.79,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.92,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,And that's why you should be\N trying to surprise me in a different way,
Comment: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.34,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,like preparing several kinds of salt.
Comment: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:56.93,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,It would have been a lot easier\N if she had just called it "boring".
Comment: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.30,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,I've been had as well.
Comment: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.81,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,The bath isn't ready yet—
Comment: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.40,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Geez, this inn is as strict as ever.
Comment: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.69,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's better to randomize cleaning times,
Comment: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,based on watching the customers' activities.
Comment: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.78,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,The good thing about a hot spring inn is being able
Comment: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to enter the hot spring whenever you like.
Comment: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.45,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Right?
Comment: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.79,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,She got me.
Comment: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.16,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,The nape of her neck was so sexy...
Comment: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.33,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Comment: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.96,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,She's a troubling customer, but...
Comment: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.42,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,But I still think she's wonderful.
Comment: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:34.72,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yeah, what she said about the cooking wasn't wrong either.
Comment: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:35.88,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.97,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,She's definitely better than that Takako that the young master always brings!
Comment: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.06,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takako says she'll be on her way!
Comment: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.43,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Die.
Comment: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.27,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Man, we're saved!
Comment: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.69,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,As long as she's here, we'll be able to handle my sister—
Comment: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:58.16,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You're going to rely on an outsider even during a situation like this?!
Comment: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.20,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,This isn't only the Kissui Inn's problem!
Comment: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.79,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,This is our problem! The Shijima's!
Comment: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:15.21,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Though she's my daughter, she's still a customer.
Comment: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:20.18,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,And that's why I didn't take charge of her room.
Comment: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.72,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,If my personal feelings get in the way,
Comment: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to do my job.
Comment: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:32.56,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,What would you do if the\N daughter of the Mikasa family were here?
Comment: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Umm...
Comment: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.49,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'd always prepare two bath towels.
Comment: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.99,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,What about for the mother?
Comment: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:42.62,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,She likes very hot tea, so I'd raise the temperature of the water in the pot.
Comment: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.41,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Comment: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.20,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,For people visiting for the first time,
Comment: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to find out about their preferences,
Comment: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.71,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,and make sure to use it for\N reference the next time they come.
Comment: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:56.42,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,But, though that customer is visiting for the first time,
Comment: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.97,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,she actually isn't.
Comment: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:03.01,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You and I know a lot about that customer.
Comment: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.65,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,They're a lot similar.
Comment: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:16.69,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,That customer and the Madam Manager, that is.
Comment: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.94,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,You think so?
Comment: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.32,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I see what you mean.
Comment: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:24.95,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,They're different kinds of people, but they have their similarities.
Comment: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell that they're mother and daughter.
Comment: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.79,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You're praising that customer too much there.
Comment: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:37.17,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,It's rude, even for the Madam Manager to take part in the kitchen's activities.
Comment: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:42.55,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,However, do you mind letting\N me use it just this once, Mr. Ren?
Comment: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.30,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Madam Manager?
Comment: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi.
Comment: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.52,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Ohana.
Comment: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.06,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Do you mind letting me prepare the futon
Comment: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for the customer in the Wisteria Room?
Comment: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.19,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.86,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Sure, but...
Comment: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.27,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.11,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Comment: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.24,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,You're back to your regular old self.
Comment: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.41,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Comment: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.16,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,My regular old self...
Comment: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.37,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.71,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you!
Comment: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.09,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wow, this is good!
Comment: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.97,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:24.22,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,A lot of effort has been put into it.
Comment: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.89,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What's this?
Comment: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:33.64,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,It's a special dish for you.
Comment: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:38.77,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Stewed fish cake is pretty plain for a dish at an inn.
Comment: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.28,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.65,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Oh... well...
Comment: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.62,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Serving my favorite food like that...
Comment: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.92,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'm using the bath, Beanman.
Comment: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.46,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Mind getting out?
Comment: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.34,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You don't need to leave.
Comment: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.59,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,A customer will be here soon.
Comment: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:07.80,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,He'll be cleaning despite whether you decide to use the bath or not.
Comment: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:08.80,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,B-But—
Comment: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.56,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be seen, wash yourself in the kitchen.
Comment: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.60,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Fine, be that way!
Comment: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.99,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Those sheets aren't dry?!
Comment: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:35.04,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I can't believe you can't sleep if\N you're not hugging rolled-up sheets.
Comment: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.54,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Then I need you to be its replacement tonight!
Comment: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.54,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Please ask your boyfriend instead.
Comment: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.05,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Is that something a daughter should be saying?
Comment: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:49.01,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You're more of a "woman" than a "mother" to me.
Comment: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.80,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That sounds cool.
Comment: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.48,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Comment: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.69,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh!
Comment: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I think it'll be better to wake her up three times.
Comment: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.61,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I agree.
Comment: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.61,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,She's not a morning person.
Comment: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.65,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Additionally...
Comment: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.95,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,She tosses about in bed!
Comment: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.70,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Yup.
Comment: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.37,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,In this area, it's cool at night even during the summer.
Comment: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.37,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Serving hot rice porridge in the morning might be a good idea.
Comment: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.12,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,And maybe we should serve\N some vegetable juice with that.
Comment: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.12,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey...
Comment: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:22.50,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I think this is the most I've spoken\N with the Madam Manager by myself.
Comment: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.63,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,And it's about Mom, too.
Comment: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.51,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,The Madam Manager is my grandmother,
Comment: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:33.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,and obviously, Mom's mother.
Comment: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.60,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Comment: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.69,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Hello?
Comment: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.31,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Mom—
Comment: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.44,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,The customer in the Wisteria Room?
Comment: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.32,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Could you bring me some sake?
Comment: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.86,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Warm, not hot.
Comment: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.15,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, and three cans of beer, please.
Comment: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.74,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Soft drinks, too.
Comment: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.57,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, and a geisha.
Comment: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.87,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,G-Geisha?!
Comment: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Well, at this hour, we can't...
Comment: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.54,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Then in that case, an old lady and a young girl will do.
Comment: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.04,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Umm...
Comment: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.71,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Comment: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.59,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're here!
Comment: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.13,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Come in and have a seat!
Comment: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.05,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry, but we still have work to do...
Comment: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.35,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't be so uptight!
Comment: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.10,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Have a glass.
Comment: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:22.73,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That was fast!
Comment: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.32,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Bravo!
Comment: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.91,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,She got drunk over soda.
Comment: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.29,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,She's really good at getting the wrong idea, after all.
Comment: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:41.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I-I knew.
Comment: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:44.54,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Okay, what did you know?
Comment: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:49.21,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I knew that Ko was important to me.
Comment: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:49.97,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.88,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you tell him so?
Comment: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,When I realized I like him,
Comment: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I got rejected!
Comment: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.81,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Comment: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:03.27,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,A woman from the Shijima family
Comment: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,giving up after being rejected once or twice?
Comment: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.07,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Comment: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:10.40,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you fought hard for Dad, Mom?
Comment: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.95,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Of course I did.
Comment: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.99,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,He was strait-laced,
Comment: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.20,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,so I was rejected four times in a row.
Comment: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,The fifth time's the charm!
Comment: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wow!
Comment: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.12,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.25,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up.
Comment: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:31.59,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I don't want to keep him at my beck and call anymore!
Comment: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko already has a life of his own.
Comment: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.05,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,In that case, do you want to come back to Tokyo?
Comment: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:43.10,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You can enter his life again.
Comment: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.73,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Comment: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:51.23,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I already have my life, too!
Comment: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:54.70,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A life at the Kissui Inn! So...
Comment: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:58.07,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,So you'd rather put work over love.
Comment: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.74,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,She really is a woman of the Shijima family.
Comment: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.50,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Though you're an exception.
Comment: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.58,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wow, I got told.
Comment: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.08,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Mom's also festing it up!
Comment: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Comment: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.96,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Both Mom and Grandma are festing it up.
Comment: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:13.51,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Fes—
Comment: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That's why...
Comment: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.97,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I also need to...
Comment: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:24.39,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Hey, having their kid recognize their effort
Comment: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,signals the end of a parent.
Comment: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.73,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,She's not listening to you.
Comment: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.91,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wow, you can hold your drink!
Comment: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.24,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Another shot, then.
Comment: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.75,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Comment: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.25,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Do I {\i1}look{\i0} like I'm working overtime?
Comment: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.05,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Comment: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.55,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed.
Comment: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.92,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,You mean Miss Satsuki?
Comment: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:59.34,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Her, Mom, and myself.
Comment: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:03.52,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'm always out of the loop.
Comment: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.27,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I can't. I ride a motorcycle.
Comment: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.98,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What a boring guy.
Comment: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.48,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Huh? Done already?
Comment: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:15.11,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I don't remember you being this weak.
Comment: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.82,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Come on, Mom.
Comment: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.29,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You'll get sick.
Comment: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.75,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I saw...
Comment: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.88,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I saw a dream.
Comment: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:39.05,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You succeeded the inn, and Ohana was there, too.
Comment: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.89,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,And then you always make me do stuff like this.
Comment: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.48,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Comment: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.98,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You okay?
Comment: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.11,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:56.82,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You're pretty light, aren't you, Mom.
Comment: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:59.28,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't make her worry too much, okay?
Comment: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.28,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I don't need you to tell me that.
Comment: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.41,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Anyway, good night.
Comment: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.59,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I didn't hear anything.
Comment: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.80,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Please continue to be that mother I always hated.
Comment: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:27.43,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything!
Comment: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.18,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Comment: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.31,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I promised.
Comment: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.23,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,If you really start hating your job, you can come back.
Comment: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.49,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,All of a sudden acting like a mother again!
Comment: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.91,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Come on, you need to let me act cool at the end.
Comment: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.66,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Take care, Beanman!
Comment: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.04,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,You too.
Comment: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:49.37,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Comment: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.51,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Hey, what's it say?!
Comment: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.72,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Come on, read it!
Comment: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.64,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Comment: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:05.51,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:13.06,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Calling it "retro" would be too simple.
Comment: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.61,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,However, without change,\N things would be too sedimented.
Comment: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:20.78,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's very difficult to get through to your customer that
Comment: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,your inn isn't going to change.
Comment: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn is always evolving,
Comment: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.54,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,in order to continue its service that is unchanging.
Comment: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.62,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,In order to protect its "retro" tradition.
Comment: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I can really tell that the staff have spirit.
Comment: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It was a very warm inn that I enjoyed staying at.
Comment: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.92,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Hey...
Comment: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.51,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,It was praise.
Comment: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.92,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Comment: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.55,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.39,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Sis...
Comment: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.27,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Beanman!
Comment: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.18,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,There, there.
Comment: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:07.07,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I realized something after Mom came here.
Comment: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.62,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Though I miss Ko,
Comment: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:17.25,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I never feel the urge to go back to Tokyo.
Comment: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.75,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's not that I'm not returning to Tokyo because things
Comment: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't the same between Ko and I.
Comment: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:26.34,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's because this place is my home.
Comment: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:30.68,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I chose this place to be my home.
Comment: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I love the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:37.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I love everyone who works here.
Comment: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:40.61,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I love Grandma, the Madam Manager,
Comment: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I also love my mother.
Comment: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:46.45,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko, too...
Comment: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:47.91,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,See ya.
Comment: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko!
Comment: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:56.50,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for everything I've done!
Comment: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.63,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything!
Comment: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.13,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Comment: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:05.55,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,See ya!
Comment: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.68,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:32.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Comment: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.22,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I even brought my swimsuit I wear during competitions.
Comment: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.22,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're going to ask her out, right?
Comment: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:38.31,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,You want to become a waitress, Ohana?
Comment: 1,0:23:38.31,0:23:41.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I don't really understand you, Yuina.
