Comment: 100,0:04:05.73,0:04:06.81,Dialogue,Nako,0,0,0,,{}Heh?
Comment: 100,0:05:38.99,0:05:39.57,Dialogue,Jiro,0,0,0,,{}Heh?
Comment: 100,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.27,Dialogue,Ohana,0,0,0,,{}Heh?
Comment: 100,0:11:53.08,0:11:53.96,Dialogue,Nako,0,0,0,,{}Heh?
Comment: 100,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.30,Dialogue,Nako,0,0,0,,{}Heh?
Comment: 100,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.09,Dialogue,Mom,0,0,0,,{}Heh?!
